description: This file initializes a React application by rendering the main <App /> component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It sets up the React root and wraps the component in React.StrictMode for highlighting potential issues.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the component tree into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the specified DOM element.
